r\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/scholarrock.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/workflow.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-780\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e7aab62 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e7aab62\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Workflow<\/h2><p>We strive for excellence by acting with integrity and operating with accountability in our work and with each other. Trust and respect are foundational to helping us achieve extraordinary results for patients.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-98f39ca h-icon elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"98f39ca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/scholarrock.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/career-development.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-779\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9e6a967 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9e6a967\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Career Development\u00a0<\/h2><p>No single team can bring a medicine to patients \u2013 we encourage our employees to collaborate with purpose and offer opportunities to apply your expertise and unique insights in new areas so you can grow in both knowledge and practice.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/di